{"id":"428835640537739_491985250889444","type":"status","created_time":"2013-06-23T18:19:04+0000","message":"The ruffians of Palashi are still hyper-active to sell out country\u2019s independence- Chhatrashibir\n\nThe Central Science and Tech Secretary of Bangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir said, \u201cthe hoodlums of Palashi are still active in this Bengal. They are still ready to sell out country\u2019s independence. A class of so-called intellectuals mainly paid by a neighboring state is trying to make this country a \u2018satellite state\u2019 and the current government is patronizing these odd fellows.\u201d\n\nHe said so while addressing as a Chief Guest to a program held by Chhatrashibir, Jagannath University Unit on the occasion of the historic Palashi Day.\n\nHe said, \u201cThis government has strayed far away with its agenda against national interest and this is why the people don\u2019t want to see it at the helm any longer.\u201d\n\nHe demanded unconditional release of all the opposition leaders including Shibir Central President without further delay."}